title: Episode 12: ‘Death Star’ With Earth Tones
dc:creator: Martin Di Caro
description: Next time you're in an underground Metro station, look up and around. Are you in a calming streetscape setting? Or does it feel more like an interstellar battle station? Historian Zachary Schrag discusses the architects’ original intent.
